# Language aware diff headers
# https://tekin.co.uk/2020/10/better-git-diff-output-for-ruby-python-elixir-and-more
# https://gist.github.com/tekin/12500956bd56784728e490d8cef9cb81
*.c     diff=cpp
*.h     diff=cpp
*.css   diff=css
*.html  diff=html
*.py    diff=python
*.md    diff=markdown

